            <div id="pageTitle">Modes of Interview</div>
            <div id="ContentText">You will be interviewing candidates using three modes, namely – campus, audio or video interviews. It is important to prepare the environment appropriately and adequately keeping in mind the mode of the interview, privacy, minimum number of distractions and comfort, not just yours but also the candidate’s. You are the face of Test My Interview's image. So Dress well.<br> <strong>Click each  mode to learn more</strong>.</div>
            
